710794f-c.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 54th Street
710794f-c.text:
Twelfth Avenue, northwest from West 54th Street, as viewed
from the northwest corner of Dewitt Clinton Park, showing
North River piers on the west side of the Avenue. At the
right isaclearance extending between 54th and 55th Streets
that is to be included in the widening of this Avenue.
April 14, 1931
March 29, 1934
P. L. Sperr
